1986", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document is a discussion of the Pcmail workstation-based distributed mail system.  It is a revision of the design published in NIC RFC-984.  The revision is based on discussion and comment fromm a variety of sources, as well as further research into the design of interactive Pcmail clients and the use of client code on machines other than IBM PCs.  As this design may change, implementation of this document is not advised.  Obsoletes RFC-984.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

